text.tspan: Yet another multi-juice beer with fruity hops?
Well, yes, but ... this atleast has real fruit in it ...
almost a smoothy ... but wait there is more!
Instead of endless sweetness this one ends in a funky
spicy mineral bitterness because of alkaline water and
a lovely yeast. Can't taste it yet?... well, just wait until
"...it is also found in Oud Bruin and Flanders red ale."
"Lambic and gueuze owe their unique flavour profiles to..."
